Ruth Stonehouse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruth_Stonehouse 0 Ruth Stonehouse (September 28, 1892 – May 12, 1941) was an actress and film director during the silent film era. Her stage career started at the age of eight as a dancer in Arizona shows. Ruth_Stonehouse ( September_28_,_1892 – May_12_,_1941 ) was an_actress_and_film_director during the_silent_film_era .
